Title: Notification spooler: Fix possible ConnectionRefusedError after update to 2.0
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: notifications
Date: 1660563193
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0p28

If the notification spooler configuration was made via "Distributed monitoring"
- "Site specific global configuration" for central sites in versions before
2.0, the start of the mknotifyd daemon could fail with an error like
"ConnectionRefusedError: [Errno 111] Connection refused".
